item.title: About
item.description: Halo, semua perkenalkan saya Wahyu Fajri Widagdo. Tetapi orang-orang terdekat saya biasa memanggil saya Edo. Untuk sementara saya isikan dulu dari section personal profile dari CV saya. I am a fresh graduate from informatics engineering major, who had an interest in web development, artificial intelligence, data mining, and business intelligence. During my studies on last semester I learn Web Development using Laravel Framework and Ruby on Rails. And I take a sidejob/part-time job after that in web development as well for experience.
